column2: SELECT p.objId,s.z, s.zErr, g.ra,g.raErr,g.dec,g.decErr,p.z,p.zErr into mydb.MyTable from PhotoObjAll as g   JOIN Photoz as p ON g.objId = p.objId   JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON g.dec = s.dec and g.ra = s.ra WHERE      p.z BETWEEN # and #      and p.photoErrorClass=#   and p.nnCount>#   and g.ra>#   and g.ra<#   and g.dec>#   and g.dec<#
